      skos:broader narr:StyleMetrics ;
      skos:note "Correction memo register. Three-section antithesis structure (wrong / correct / scope). Short punchy declaratives at key retraction moments ('There is no [amount] Tranche 2.'). Active voice dominant. Jargon density moderate — financial terms (SAFE, SEL, SAFE + SEL, tranche, envelope, dilution) used without definition, implying internal audience. Sentence length elevated in the 'What's correct' section by the staircase-discipline explanation; retraction sections are shorter and more direct." ;
